6
00:01:02.855 --> 00:01:03.981
- [guard shouts]
- [Irina yelps]

7
00:01:05.147 --> 00:01:08.026
- [door closes. locks]
- [Irina grunts]

8
00:01:08.944 --> 00:01:10.320
[groans]

9
00:01:11.321 --> 00:01:13.323
- [panting]
- [water dripping]

10
00:01:15.951 --> 00:01:17.035
